        {
            "title": "油價高收近約3%　紐約期油曾升穿60美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">油價日內觸及逾1個月高位，英美期油收市升近3%或以上。隨著美國與英國達成貿易協議，市場憧憬中美會談取得突破。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-4.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-4.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油曾升穿60美元但未企穩，收報59.91美元，升1.84美元，升幅3.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油高見每桶63.36美元，收市報62.84美元，升1.72美元，升幅2.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，市場警告，關稅引發的石油市場波動仍未結束。而若果美國與伊朗達成核協議，全球油供應增加，將拖累油價表現，花旗預料布蘭特期油或跌至50美元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14914428-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6%e8%bf%91%e7%b4%843%e3%80%80%e7%b4%90%e7%b4%84%e6%9c%9f%e6%b2%b9%e6%9b%be%e5%8d%87%e7%a9%bf60%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230704-100638_20230704_fi_source-AP_OilPrice_source-ap_-1-1-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 08:46:00",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "德股高收1%創近兩月新高　英股連跌兩日",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市普遍上升，英國股市偏軟。英國與美國達成貿易協議，另外，英倫銀行一如預期減息0.25厘，指標利率降至4.25厘。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：德國證交所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數反覆向下，收市報8531點，跌27點，跌幅0.32%，連跌兩日。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德法股市則反彈，德國DAX指數收報23352點，升236點，升幅1.02%，創近兩個月新高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報7694點，升67點，升幅0.89%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報38974點，躍高1.71%或654點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報13488點，微升0.06%或8點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英倫銀行議息後宣布減息四分一厘，符合市場預期，行長貝利(Andrew Bailey)表示，通脹緩解壓力允許減息，但央行需要堅持「循序漸進、謹慎」的做法。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14914440-%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b61%e5%89%b5%e8%bf%91%e5%85%a9%e6%9c%88%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e3%80%80%e8%8b%b1%e8%82%a1%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c%e5%85%a9%e6%97%a5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 08:46:03",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "道指高收254點納指升1%　航空股急升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股連升兩日，美國與英國達成貿易協議，利好投資情緒，市場正觀望中美貿易會談發展。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數高開198點後，美國總統特朗普表示，「你最好現在就出去買股票」，這番言論發表後，道指升幅擴大至最多659點，高見41773點；收市報41368點，升254點，升幅0.62%，創逾5星期新高。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標普500指數收報5663點，升32點，升幅0.58%，一度上揚1.58%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數一度升穿18000點關口，漲2.02%，高見18096點，收市報17928點，升189點，升幅1.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美英協議豁免勞斯萊斯生產的飛機零部件關稅，帶動航空股急升，美國航空、聯合航空、達美航空升逾4%至逾7%。波音升3.3%，是表現最好道指成份股，英國將購買價值100億美元的波音飛機。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國計劃撤銷先進人工智能(AI)晶片出口限制，晶片股大多延續上日升勢，AMD、博通、英特爾升逾1%至逾3%，Nvidia微升，英國晶片設計公司安謀(ARM)今季收入預測遜色，股價下瀉6.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">特斯拉(Tesla)及Alphabet股價收市分別漲3.1%及1.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Coach母公司Tapestry調高全年業績展望，股價抽高3.7%；電商平台Shopify預測今季盈利放慢，股價插水6.7%，收市只跌0.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14914409-%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6254%e9%bb%9e%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%871%e3%80%80%e8%88%aa%e7%a9%ba%e8%82%a1%e6%80%a5%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20200617_FI_US-STOCK_FB-2-1-1-2-1-1-1-2-1-1-1-2-1_source-ap_-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 08:40:58",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "彭博 : 內地考慮不允許樓花預售",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》報道，內地正考慮徹底改革全國住宅樓宇銷售，規定發展商不得進行樓花預售，只能出售已建成樓宇。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source_licensed_China-Property_shutterstock-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source_licensed_China-Property_shutterstock-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道引述消息人士稱，這是中央政策建房地產市場發展新模式一部份，而樓花銷被視為加劇當前樓市危機的因素。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新措施只適用於實行之後批出的土地，且不包括公共樓宇項目，報道指，地方政府執行該項政策有一定酌情。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">分析指該項政策的主要目標，是限制新樓推出市場，令樓價穩定，三四線城市或較廣泛實行這項政策。不過，取消樓花預售，將增加發展商現金流壓力，日後買地將趨向審慎，導至在房地產市場投資持續減少。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14913526-%e5%bd%ad%e5%8d%9a-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e8%80%83%e6%85%ae%e4%b8%8d%e5%85%81%e8%a8%b1%e6%a8%93%e8%8a%b1%e9%a0%90%e5%94%ae",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230901_FI_China-Property_source_web_-shutterstock_1200.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 17:46:24",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "東風集團今年首4個月銷量按年降20.8% 新能源車銷售則升27.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東風集團(00489)公布，今年首4個月累計汽車銷量52.67萬輛，按年下降20.8%，其中新能源車銷售則按年增27.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內該公司新能源車銷售12.04萬輛。母公司東風汽車集團期內累計銷量則達65.11萬輛，按年降23.3%；東風集團旗下於內地A股上市的東風汽車股份，今年首4個月累計銷售4.98萬輛，按年減少約14.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14913396-%e6%9d%b1%e9%a2%a8%e9%9b%86%e5%9c%98%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e9%a6%964%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e9%8a%b7%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d20-8-%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90%e8%bb%8a%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e5%89%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/00486-2024.jpg.webp",
